---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Tanush Paradeshi</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #ffffff;
        --text: #111827;
        --muted: #4b5563; /* readable gray */
        --border: #e5e7eb;
        --card: #ffffff;
        --shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.06), 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        --radius: 14px;

        /* link styling */
        --link: #2563eb;
        --link-hover: #1d4ed8;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 980px;
        margin: 56px auto;
        padding: 0 18px;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      h1, h2, h3 {
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 34px;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin: 0;
      }

      h2 {
        margin-top: 26px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 20px;
      }

      h3 {
        font-size: 16px;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
      }

      hr {
        border: 0;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
        margin: 22px 0;
      }

      .header {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
      }

      .section-block {
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      /* Make links look like links */
      a {
        color: var(--link);
        text-decoration: underline;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
        text-decoration-thickness: 1px;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      a:hover {
        color: var(--link-hover);
      }

      /* Header links look like pills */
      .toplinks a {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #fafafa;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .toplinks a:hover {
        background: #f3f4f6;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      /* Grid/cards */
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      @media (min-width: 860px) {
        .grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }
      }

      .card {
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        padding: 16px;
        background: var(--card);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 6px 0;
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0 0 12px 0;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      /* Project links row */
      .links {
        margin-top: 2px;
      }

      .links a {
        margin-right: 12px;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      /* Lists */
      ul {
        margin: 8px 0 0 18px;
      }

      li {
        margin: 6px 0;
      }

      /* Skills should be full contrast */
      .skills-text {
        color: var(--text);
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 46px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <main class="container">
      <header class="header">
        <h1>Tanush Paradeshi</h1>

        <!-- About text is FULL CONTRAST (not muted) -->
        <p>
          Hello, I’m Tanush. I’m a sophomore at Carnegie Mellon University studying computer science and statistical machine learning. I enjoy building things across web and mobile development, machine learning, and data science, with projects spanning computer vision, bioinformatics, and computational modeling of physical systems. I’m particularly interested in math, probability, and algorithms, and I’ve also spent time doing competitive math and programming.
        </p>

        <p class="toplinks">
          <a href="https://github.com/tanu1239">GitHub</a> ·
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tanush-paradeshi-638754214">LinkedIn</a> ·
          <a href="/resume.pdf">Resume</a> ·
          <a href="mailto:tparades@andrew.cmu.edu">Email</a>
        </p>
      </header>

      <hr />

      <section class="section-block">
        <h2>Education</h2>
        <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>Carnegie Mellon University</strong></p>
        <p style="margin-top: 6px;">B.S. Computer Science + Statistics/Machine Learning (edit as needed)</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 16px;">Relevant Coursework</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Data Structures & Algorithms (15-122)</li>
          <li>Introduction to Computer Systems (15-213)</li>
          <li>Functional Programming (15-150)</li>
          <li>Parallel & Sequential Data Structures and Algorithms (15-210)</li>
          <li>Great Theoretical Ideas in Computer Science (15-251)</li>
          <li>Discrete Mathematics (21-127)</li>
          <li>Linear Algebra (21-241)</li>
          <li>Multivariable Calculus (21-259)</li>
          <li>Probability Theory (21-325)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="section-block">
        <h2>Skills</h2>

        <h3 style="margin: 10px 0 6px 0;">Proficient Programming Languages</h3>
        <p class="skills-text">{skills.languages.join(", ")}</p>

        <h3 style="margin: 14px 0 6px 0;">Packages / Software</h3>
